import React from 'react' const Rating = ({value,text}) => { return (
=1?'fas fa-star':value>=0.5?'fas fa-star-half-alt':'far fa-star'}/> =2?'fas fa-star':value>=1.5?'fas fa-star-half-alt':'far fa-star'}/> =3?'fas fa-star':value>=2.5?'fas fa-star-half-alt':'far fa-star'}/> =4?'fas fa-star':value>=3.5?'fas fa-star-half-alt':'far fa-star'}/> {text && text}
) } export default Rating
